{"tid":1028931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"挪威國會議員提名川普角逐諾貝爾和平奬","createTime":"2019-02-20T00:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T05:54:31.000Z","uid":141151,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3467b227ef739f4ba14f6d708ad9567a6edfab8e","tid":1028931,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T00:42:31.000Z","msg":"挪威國會議員提名川普角逐諾貝爾和平奬<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8C%AA%E5%A8%81%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%8F%90%E5%90%8D%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E8%A7%92%E9%80%90%E8%AB%BE%E8%B2%9D%E7%88%BE%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E5%A5%AC-105619121.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%258C%25AA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%25B7%259D%25E6%2599%25AE%25E8%25A7%2592%25E9%2580%2590%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E8%25B2%259D%25E7%2588%25BE%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%25A5%25AC-105619121.html&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZ5nDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=b8362955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8C%AA%E5%A8%81%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%8F%90%E5%90%8D%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E8%A7%92%E9%80%90%E8%AB%BE%E8%B2%9D%E7%88%BE%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E5%A5%AC-105619121.html</a><br />\n<br />\n（路透華盛頓18日電）兩名挪威國會議員已提名美國總統川普角逐諾貝爾和平獎，以肯定他促進朝鮮半島情勢的正面發展。<br />\n<br />\n2016到2018年曾在挪威總理索爾伯格（Erna Solberg）內閣擔任司法部長的阿蒙森（Per-Willy Amundsen）告訴路透社：「我們提名他當然是因為朝鮮半島的正面發展。」<br />\n<br />\n他還說：「原本局勢非常艱難，之後緊張降低，很大程度是因為川普的非典型外交作風。」<br />\n<br />\n右翼「進步黨」（Progress Party）籍的阿蒙森表示，他與同是國會議員的泰布林吉加德（Christian Tybring-Gjedde）聯合致函挪威諾貝爾委員會，時間就在去年6月川普剛與北韓領導人金正恩在新加坡舉行峰會後。<br />\n<br />\n2019年諾貝爾和平獎提名截止日期在1月31日，10月11日將宣布得主。中央社（翻譯）"},{"pid":"2f0e96980247d903cb2c18216f058f7b024170da","tid":1028931,"uid":14918,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T00:47:29.000Z","msg":"挪威又提名<br />\n日本又提"},{"pid":"e918d7e6c2a1ace5c5c844d5ef2fe97da304b760","tid":1028931,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T00:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12afed2145b8baf0315a38e6362434e50c7f1d5","tid":1028931,"uid":121146,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"2f0e96980247d903cb2c18216f058f7b024170da","tid":1028931,"uid":14918,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T00:47:29.000Z","msg":"挪威又提名<br />\n日本又提"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T00:50:04.000Z","msg":"前幾日左膠報: 係美國迫安倍提名佢架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次應該係美國威迫挪威 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4190a0be9e66a9878f5338f39159f3ef9a58cdf3","tid":1028931,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:04:11.000Z","msg":"晨早要"},{"pid":"6d36540665491a62b029dd0124458cae08c43ac6","tid":1028931,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec746560211eb665b64a5d6d1d8c1ac1ff59735a","tid":1028931,"uid":121146,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:19:07.000Z","msg":"反侵者而家一昧話北韓未真棄核<br />\n但佢地係咪唔記得左北韓以前隔個月射一支導彈？"},{"pid":"080f2b0e50b308a70848a8b3953350d4d686e3d6","tid":1028931,"uid":550,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ec746560211eb665b64a5d6d1d8c1ac1ff59735a","tid":1028931,"uid":121146,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:19:07.000Z","msg":"反侵者而家一昧話北韓未真棄核<br />\n但佢地係咪唔記得左北韓以前隔個月射一支導彈？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:54:31.000Z","msg":"最好笑係佢地踩侵要見多次金仔<br />\n又唔睇下奧巴馬乜都冇做就有獎<br />\n見下古巴個總理當年就吹到幾咁偉大<br />\n橫睇掂睇 侵金會對廿一世紀嘅意義重大好多啦"}]}